#   - Cateogry: movies
#   - Priority: Normal or Low (Keep on Normal if you want movies over tv shows; low if you want TV shows first to download)
#  - KickassTorrents: Off
#  - Torrentz: Off
#  - Newznab:  You will need at least one provider. See root area for a file called "Indexers".
#  - Rename Movies: On
#   - Cleanup: Check the BOX [ON]
#   - To: /mnt/rclone-union/zilch/movies/                  (note: this may take awhile to load up)
#   - From: /mnt/sab/downloads/complete/movies/            (note: blank? it's because you need to wait for 1st load up to finish)
